                        ul.list-group.list-group-flush
                            li.list-group-item.text-white.bg-primary.py-5 #[strong Customization:] We can design a training program that is tailored specifically to your goals, fitness level, and individual needs. This can be much more effective than following a generic workout plan or trying to figure out what to do on your own. 
                            li.list-group-item.text-white.bg-primary.py-5 #[strong Expert guidance:] We are trained professionals who can provide expert guidance on proper form, technique, and nutrition to help you get the most out of your workouts. This can help you avoid common mistakes and injuries, and ensure that you are on the right track to achieving your goals.
                            li.list-group-item.text-white.bg-primary.py-5 #[strong Motivation and accountability:] Having a relationship with one of our trainers can provide a great source of motivation and accountability, helping you stay on track and stay committed to your fitness journey.
                            li.list-group-item.text-white.bg-primary.py-5 #[strong Flexibility:] We can work with you to schedule workouts that fit your schedule and lifestyle, and can provide a range of training options to suit your preferences.

